WEBVTT

00:07:29.284 --> 00:07:30.438
Right?

00:07:30.462 --> 00:07:33.803
Is that something like
what we imagine or assume?

00:07:34.613 --> 00:07:36.217
And under that kind of scenario,

00:07:36.241 --> 00:07:39.600
it's all a big, tragic misunderstanding.

00:07:41.334 --> 00:07:43.444
But it seems that's wrong.

00:07:44.397 --> 00:07:47.258
First of all, race is a recent invention.

00:07:47.282 --> 00:07:49.084
It's just a few hundred years old.

00:07:49.892 --> 00:07:53.521
Before that, yes,
people divided themselves

00:07:53.545 --> 00:07:57.439
by religion, tribal group, language,

00:07:57.463 --> 00:07:58.635
things like that.

00:07:58.659 --> 00:08:00.103
But for most of human history,